      "message": "[Critical] Line 270: The generated meson wrapper is not valid shell: `exec PYTHONPATH\u003d... python3 ...` attempts to exec a program named `PYTHONPATH\u003d...` instead of setting the environment. Meson will fail to start from this toolchain. Export PYTHONPATH before exec, preserving any existing value. Suggested fix:\n```suggestion\n\tprintf \u0027#!/bin/sh\\nexport PYTHONPATH\u003d\"$(PREFIX)/lib/meson-packages$${PYTHONPATH:+:$$PYTHONPATH}\"\\nexec python3 -m mesonbuild \"$$@\"\\n\u0027 \\\n\t\t\u003e $(PREFIX)/bin/meson\n```",
      "revId": "bad686d9b41474309af9e66cfb987a0e0b56435e",
