      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 1269: The normal SwarmMessageUpdated emission was removed from handleEdition and is now only emitted from the plugin path when ENABLE_PLUGIN is enabled and plugin handlers exist. This means ordinary message edits will no longer update clients when plugins are disabled or no chat handler is active. Restore the baseline update signal independently of plugin processing, and only add plugin overwrite injection as an enhancement. Suggested fix:\n```suggestion\n                emitSignal\u003clibjami::ConversationSignal::SwarmMessageUpdated\u003e(\n                    accountId_, repository_-\u003eid(), injectEditionOverwrites(*it-\u003esecond, history.quickAccess));\n```",
      "revId": "bad686d9b41474309af9e66cfb987a0e0b56435e",
